--- a/MAINTAINERS
+++ b/MAINTAINERS
@@ -9022,6 +9022,7 @@ M:	Rajneesh Bhardwaj <irenic.rajneesh@gmail.com>
 M:	David E Box <david.e.box@intel.com>
